\section{Conclusions and next steps}

\begin{frame}
\frametitle{Conclusions and next steps}

\bi
\item We derived a comparable scale of non-cognitive skills / behaviour problems
\item We have shown that inequality (across the income dimension) has increased
  \bi
  \item Profile has become steeper (particularly for males)
  \item Scores at upper quantiles have drifted upwards
  \ei
\pause
\vspace{12pt}
\item Next steps
  \bi
  \item Harmonise more cohorts (NCDS) and ages (10)
  \item Extend analysis to the \emph{returns} to non-cognitive skills -- are they remunerated differently on the labour market?
  \ei
\ei

\end{frame}

